Interface EventActionIfc<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type associated with the JSLEvent's message property Implementor's of this interface should define a class that has concrete specification for the type T.

    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
    @FunctionalInterface
public interface EventActionIfc<T>
    An interface used to implement the actions associated with event logic within the simulation.
